title: section 33(1) of the Finance Act 2021 (No. 45 of 2021) comes into operation.
heading: 2. The 16th day of November 2022 is appointed as the day on which
text_raw:
2. The 16th day of November 2022 is appointed as the day on which 

section 33(1) of the Finance Act 2021 (No. 45 of 2021) comes into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

10 November, 2022. 

PASCHAL DONOHOE, 
Minister for Finance. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 18th November, 2022.
